data.description: Calling all investors and first-time home buyers!  Located on a dead-end street and nestled on a fabulous 280 ft. deep lot! This 3 bedroom 1 bathroom colonial was all re-done in 2018. This included roof & gutters, furnace & air,  windows & exterior doors, new siding & front steps, and some new plumbing & lighting. This home is close to shopping and expressway access. This one won't last long make sure to set up your private showing today.
